                    <h2>Wifi Controlled Power Bar</h2>
                    <hr class="small">
                    <p class="lead">This box acts as a power bar with four outlets that can be turned on and off individually. 
                    The Wi-Fi enabled microcontroller allows me to control the outlets from anywhere via my website. 
                    It can be used with anything that normally plugs into a wall outlet, so long as the current stays under 10A. </p>
                    <hr class="small">
